			<div class="content" id="post-content-3865615">
									

<p>This first Log of Anomalous Items, grown and groomed over the past nine years, is now locked for further edits and a <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/log-of-anomalous-items-vol-ii">second log</a> is now open for business.</p>
<p>Thank you to all the wonderful authors over the years to have contributed to the first log, and many thanks to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/absentmindednihilist" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2812984); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2812984&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1530979557" alt="AbsentmindedNihilist" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2812984)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/absentmindednihilist" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2812984); return false;">AbsentmindedNihilist</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/modern-erasmus" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3129691); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3129691&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1530979557" alt="Modern_Erasmus" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3129691)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/modern-erasmus" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3129691); return false;">Modern_Erasmus</a></span>, and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/veiedhimaedhr" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3737554); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3737554&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1530979557" alt="Veiedhimaedhr" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3737554)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/veiedhimaedhr" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3737554); return false;">Veiedhimaedhr</a></span> who did the heavy lifting of the final prune, along with longtime crit experts and pruners <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/zyn" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1404533); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1404533&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1530979557" alt="Zyn" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1404533)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/zyn" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1404533); return false;">Zyn</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dexanote" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(481882); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=481882&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1530979557" alt="Dexanote" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=481882)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dexanote" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(481882); return false;">Dexanote</a></span>, and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/stormbreath" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3075960); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3075960&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1530979557" alt="stormbreath" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3075960)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/stormbreath" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3075960); return false;">stormbreath</a></span> who helped make it happen.</p>

